Package: agentr
Type: Package
Title: Specification and Review Scaffolding for Agentic Workflows in R
Version: 0.2.7.10
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver", 
           family = "Zhou",
           email = "oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Specification, review, and scaffolding helpers for agentic AI systems.
    The package standardizes workflow, memory, knowledge, interface, proposal,
    and review artifacts so humans and coding assistants can infer, inspect,
    revise, and hand off agentic task designs. It intentionally excludes
    communication backends, provider-specific LLM client code, and full runtime
    execution engines so that design artifacts and implementation transport
    remain cleanly separated.
